            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">And best of all, it comes with source! Since we’ll have the source code that generates the CAPTCHAs, this should be pretty easy to break. To make things a little more challenging, let’s give ourself a time limit. Can we fully break this CAPTCHA system in less than 15 minutes? Let’s try it!</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
